list.name: Repo
list.query: match(n:GIT:DATA) where  n.repoName in ["agency_gateway_ui"] return distinct n.repoName as Repo

list.name: Branch
list.query: match(n:GIT:DATA) where   n.branchName<>"null" return distinct n.branchName as Branch

targets.target: match(n:GIT:DATA) where (tofloat(n.inSightsTime)>=?START_TIME? AND tofloat(n.inSightsTime)<=?END_TIME?) and  (n.repoName in $Repo) and (n.branchName in $Branch)   with n as n,split(n.inSightsTimeX,'T')[0] as time return time,count(n.commitId) as count order by time

match(n:GIT:DATA) where (tofloat(n.inSightsTime)>=?START_TIME? AND tofloat(n.inSightsTime)<=?END_TIME?) and  (n.repoName in $Repo) and (n.branchName in $Branch)   return count(n.commitId) as count,count(distinct n.authorName) as count1

match(m:GIT:DATA) where (tofloat(m.inSightsTime)>=?START_TIME? AND tofloat(m.inSightsTime)<=?END_TIME?) and  (m.repoName in $Repo) and (m.branchName in $Branch)
with m,
CASE WHEN m.authorName="Matt Howell"
THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as MattHowell,
CASE WHEN m.authorName="Jenkins Automation Server"
THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as JenkinsAutomationServer,
CASE WHEN m.authorName="cakersrailroad"
THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as cakersrailroad,
CASE WHEN m.authorName="Matt"
THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as Matt,
CASE WHEN m.authorName="Mattie J"
THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as MattieJ,
CASE WHEN m.authorName="Chandra Pasupuleti"
THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as ChandraPasupuleti
return  split(m.inSightsTimeX,'T')[0] as inSightsTime,sum(MattHowell) as MattHowell,sum(JenkinsAutomationServer) as JenkinsAutomationServer,sum(cakersrailroad) as cakersrailroad,sum(Matt) as Matt,sum(MattieJ) as MattieJ,sum(ChandraPasupuleti) as ChandraPasupuleti  order by inSightsTime

match(n:GIT:DATA) where n.repoName="agency_gateway_ui"  AND (tofloat(n.inSightsTime)>=?START_TIME? AND tofloat(n.inSightsTime)<=?END_TIME?)  and  (n.branchName in $Branch) return n.authorName,count(n.commitId) as count
match(n:SCM:GIT:DATA)  where n.inSightsTime>(timestamp()/1000)-1*86400   and  (n.repoName in $Repo) and (n.branchName in $Branch)   return count(n.commitId) as Last24Hrs
match(n:SCM:GIT:DATA)  where n.inSightsTime>(timestamp()/1000)-7*86400  and  (n.repoName in $Repo) and (n.branchName in $Branch)   return count(n.commitId) as Last7Days
match(n:SCM:GIT:DATA)  where n.inSightsTime>(timestamp()/1000)-14*86400  and  (n.repoName in $Repo) and (n.branchName in $Branch)   return count(n.commitId) as Last14Days

match(m:CI:JENKINS:DATA) where exists(m.result)   and m.jobName IN ["Build_Dev", "Build_QA","Build_QA_Branch_Merge" ,"Build_Stage"] AND (tofloat(m.inSightsTime)>=?START_TIME? AND tofloat(m.inSightsTime)<=?END_TIME?)
with m,
CASE WHEN m.result="SUCCESS"
THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as success,
CASE 
WHEN m.result="FAILURE" OR m.result="UNSTABLE" 
THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as failure
return split(m.inSightsTimeX,'T')[0] as inSightsTime,sum(success) as Success, sum(failure) as Failure  order by inSightsTime asc

match(m:CI:JENKINS:DATA) where exists(m.result)   and m.jobName IN ["Build_Dev", "Build_QA","Build_QA_Branch_Merge" ,"Build_Stage"] AND (tofloat(m.inSightsTime)>=?START_TIME? AND tofloat(m.inSightsTime)<=?END_TIME?) 
with m,
CASE WHEN m.result="SUCCESS"
THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as success,
CASE 
WHEN m.result="FAILURE" OR m.result="UNSTABLE" 
THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as failure
return sum(success) as Success, sum(failure) as Failure

MATCH(n:CI:JENKINS:DATA) where n.jobName in ["Build_Dev", "Build_QA", "Build_QA_Branch_Merge", "Build_Stage"]  AND tofloat(n.inSightsTime)>=?START_TIME? AND tofloat(n.inSightsTime)<=?END_TIME? with n,
CASE WHEN n.result='SUCCESS'
then n.duration else 0 End as success,
CASE WHEN n.result='FAILURE' OR n.result="UNSTABLE" 
THEN n.duration else 0 End as failure
return split(n.inSightsTimeX,'T')[0] as inSightsTime,ceil(avg(toInt(success/1000/60))) as SuccessAvgDuration,ceil(avg(toInt(failure/1000/60))) as FailureAvgDuration  order by inSightsTime asc

match(n:CI:JENKINS:DATA)    where n.jobName IN ["Build_Dev", "Build_QA", "Build_QA_Branch_Merge" ,"Build_Stage"] with  n.jobName as jobName,n.result as result,n.buildNumber as buildNumber,ceil(avg(toInt(n.duration/1000/60))) as AvgDuration,split(n.inSightsTimeX,"Z")[0] as BuildTime,collect(distinct n.buildUrl) as buildURL,toInt(n.inSightsTime) as time,n.shortDescription as Description OPTIONAL match(m:CI:JENKINS:DATA)   where m.jobName=split(split(Description,'Started by upstream project "Agency_Gateway_UI/')[1],'"')[0] and m.buildNumber=split(split(Description,'Started by upstream project "Agency_Gateway_UI/UI_Config_Validation')[1],'build number ')[1]  return jobName,result,collect(distinct buildNumber) as buildNumber,AvgDuration,split(m.shortDescription,',')[0]  as BuildType,BuildTime,buildURL,Description,time order by time desc limit 5
